text: Rishi Ketan Patel (born 26 July 1998) is an English cricketer. He has played for Essex's Second XI side, and signed a professional contract with Essex in 2018. He made his first-class debut on 26 March 2019, for Cambridge MCCU against Essex, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. He made his List A debut on 28 April 2019, for Essex in the 2019 Royal London One-Day Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge MCCU cricketers Category:Essex cricketers Category:People from Chigwell Category:Hertfordshire cricketers
